{"tid":341873,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(拋磚引玉)由細到大做過最痴線嘅嘢係咩？","createTime":"2017-07-31T07:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T08:24:38.000Z","uid":130402,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b868466ed7304d2d6999ce2a9e85f034aee4e60f","tid":341873,"uid":130402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:05:33.000Z","msg":"我試過細個好急屎，全屋得媽咪一個但佢都霸左廁所<br />\n我忍到忍無可忍，就翻埋自己間房鎖門，開窗屙屎出街。嗰陣仲要係屙爛屎，請到窗花同埋樓下單位嘅冷氣機都係啡色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我都好乖仔抹返返個窗花，樓下個冷氣機就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過見幾日之後樓下個單位換咗新冷氣機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c9c0b6092c45b07238e2e832e8c0701d771f7f","tid":341873,"uid":92201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:12:54.000Z","msg":"屌你, 隔住個mon再隔埋個窗都有陣屎味"},{"pid":"4cc241317acb54c7e8b746770bb2e4acda4d74b7","tid":341873,"uid":130402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:28:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你, 隔住個mon再隔埋個窗都有陣屎味</blockquote><br />\n你又做過啲咩癡線野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff81347d7d9806a45309dc79483c0513fc1fd2a4","tid":341873,"uid":9483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:30:25.000Z","msg":"唔抄答案做哂成本暑期作業<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa10a88fad9ecea30c3ded4d8f8ed98428802ba","tid":341873,"uid":84049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T07:34:07.000Z","msg":"屙塞左朋友屋企個廁所，用廁所揼都冇用<br />\n之後俾左兩個膠袋我，一執起就掉左落街<br />